## Component Customization

Kibo UI components are added directly to your codebase, allowing for:

- Easy customization and extension
- Full control over component behavior
- Seamless integration with your design system
- TypeScript support with proper type definitions

## When to Use Kibo UI vs shadcn/ui

- **Use Kibo UI components** for advanced functionality (Gantt charts, Kanban boards, enhanced calendars, etc.)
- **Use standard shadcn/ui components** for basic UI elements (Button, Input, Dialog, etc.)
- **Combine both** for comprehensive UI coverage

## Built on shadcn/ui

Kibo UI is built on top of shadcn/ui, so all standard shadcn/ui components are also available.
Components are designed to work together seamlessly with consistent styling and behavior.
